title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-21-2014 TUES
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-21-2014 TUES





Eclipse of Man
Bookmark and Share
 
 
Posted Tuesday, October 21st 2014 @ 5pm

01PM - 03PM 10-21-2014

 

1. Mike reads column by Harvard Yiddish scholar, 
     Ruth Wisse "Vote for Tom Cotton-and Redeem Harvard.
      The Army veteran is also an alum of a school that needs 
        to have its patriotic bona fides buffed." 

2. Mike deconstructs letter to the editor criticizing the 
    Denver Post for endorsing Mike Coffman. 

3. Megyn Kelly interview with the lawyer for the 
    Fort Hood shooter. 

4. NY Times admits that Bush was right about WMD in Iraq. 

5. Guest: Charles T. Rubin, author of 

    "Eclipse of Man: Human Extinction and the Meaning of Progress."
